@startuml Nebras_SDK_Sequence_Diagram
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10

actor "Developer / App" as App
box "Nebras Java SDK" #LightCyan
participant "ConsentManager" as Consent
participant "ApiTokenizationService" as Tokenizer
participant "NebrasClient" as Client
participant "NebrasIntentMapper" as Mapper
participant "WorkflowWatcher" as Watcher
end box

box "Agentive Platform" #LightGoldenRodYellow
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
end box

== 1. Consent Management (SCA) ==
App -> Consent : initiateConsentFlow("DOMESTIC_PAYMENT")
Consent --> App : Redirect URL (https://auth.opf...)
note over App : User authorizes payment\nvia UAE Pass / Mobile App
App -> Consent : checkConsentStatus(consentId)
Consent --> App : status = AUTHORIZED

== 2. API Tokenization ==
App -> Tokenizer : exchangeConsentForToken(consentId)
Tokenizer --> App : api_token

== 3. Payment Execution ==
App -> Client : executeSalaryBatch(SalaryBatchRequest)
Client -> Mapper : mapToOpenFinanceIntent(SalaryBatchRequest)
Mapper --> Client : JSON Payload
Client -> Client : generateDpopProof(privateKey)
Client -> Gateway : POST /domestic-payments\nHeaders: [Authorization: Bearer api_token, DPoP: proof]
Gateway --> Client : intentId
Client --> App : intentId

== 4. Agentive Polling ==
App -> Watcher : waitForCompletion(intentId)
note over Watcher : Polls status until\nTemporal Agents finish
Watcher --> App : COMPLETED_SUCCESSFULLY

@enduml
